## 📁 Project Structure (Planned)

```bash
machine-learning-project/
│
├── data/                     # Sample datasets (CSV, JSON, etc.)
├── notebooks/                # Jupyter notebooks for learning & experimentation
├── models/                   # Saved models (Pickle, Joblib, etc.)
├── deployment/               # Web app integration (Flask/Streamlit)
├── utils/                    # Helper functions (e.g., preprocessing, visualization)
├── reports/                  # EDA reports and model evaluations
├── machine-learning-roadmap-v2.pdf
└── README.md
